name: Power is closer than close
description:
Power is closer is the "mandala" piece layer used with "Travelling for power" a previous NFT piece listed here.

It's almost like a depiction of getting strength while still using it. Losing and getting, training and exhausting but always striving for better. Like an "aura" you might know is always out there to work with.

Pumping and extracting. It's so close to my heart oh man.
